name: No. 2 (Orange, Yellow and Grey)
description:
Part of a collection of color field items, this piece is a gateway. A door through which viewers could pass into a world of perception where mythic dramas can be accessed by the emotions. 

This piece seems to glow from within, as if generating its own light, as if some mysterious space exists within it and the light from that space is emanating into this dimension through a clouded glass.
